<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>والغَشاوَةِ، وقرأَ زيدُ بن عليٍّ والحَسَنُ،<span class="c5"> واليَمانِيّ:</span> <span class="c2">(وَعلَى أَبْصَارِهمْ غُشَاوة)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(العَشاوةُ)</span> العَشاوَةُ: العَشَى.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وقرأَ طاوُوس:</span> <span class="c2">(وَعَلَى أَبْصَارِهِم عَشَاوَةٌ)</span> وكذلك <span class="c2">(وَجَعَلَ عَلَى بَصَرهِ عَشَاوَةً)</span> .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(أَخدع)</span> أَخْدَعَه: حَمَله على<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>